{"tid":1610504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10.1 港島 入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:49:34.000Z","uid":288162,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e78cbc01f0c566900e16624ce775ec60ee6cf9","tid":1610504,"uid":288162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"有泛民大台吹雞，係多和理嘅，係開心嘅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一，唔諗住留/打嘅要沿路返灣仔老銅，和理嘅力量就係人多就唔會比狗咬，要守住退路，夏慤冇嘢好睇<br />\n<br />\n二，幾時都要alert，對恃緊就咪撚唱肥媽咪撚嗌口號住<br />\n<br />\n三，叫你走就真係要一二一二快步走，你唔走前線退唔到，你走咗安全咗唔繼續向前再走，前線一樣冇位走<br />\n<br />\n四，出嚟就咪撚掛住打卡，夠膽死兵荒馬亂三邊比狗夾緊都仲停底影火魔法打卡<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">合和拉得最多係連豬咀都冇嘅和理呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n五，全民換衫做街坊，多你一個屌狗會安全好多<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">街坊屌狗人人有責</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後大隊返老銅再比洗地車推去天后炮台山，同時有手足有街坊喺sogo向東屌返班狗係靚move<br />\n逼到佢放煙花之餘冇送頭<br />\n最緊要係buy time比大隊散，冇得銅鑼灣炮台山夾<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放煙花賀佢老母點可以冇老銅份</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後最後，北角白衣人鬼伏事件<br />\n屌，講咗幾多次EQ要高咪撚送頭，入夜少咗一大半手足，白衣人出嚟企街咪由鳩佢，咪撚睇少啲叔輩街坊先得㗎<br />\n狗狗依家鐘意打空氣，咪由鳩得佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結港島戰線<br />\n失策，需改善，需部署<br />\n<br />\n岳巴話齋<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">留得青山在哪怕冇柴燒</span></span><br />\n場仗有排打，應守則守撚完好走"},{"pid":"a889ecb986035120b756c2b51bb85875fe63979d","tid":1610504,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:00:12.000Z","msg":"請全民無&middot;限&middot;期罷工罷課，救自己、救義士！迫政府讓步！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"91fe5980126f1c2ac5ec7b9bc87acaa183042a2d","tid":1610504,"uid":229733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:49:34.000Z","msg":"港島班和理非又要做引戰狗 <br />\n但又第一個跑走<br />\n<br />\n打咗冇耐 遠距離見到畜龍就走<br />\n得果小小勇武手足邊夠打<br />\n仲要被包抄<br />\n走又唔識調返轉望住班狗走<br />\n個個自己跑 逼撚到沙甸魚咁 <br />\n講咗有狗 唔好上山 有啲傻閪又唔聽<br />\n<br />\n不如返屋企啦好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲仲on9 屌返我地轉頭<br />\n出咗火魔法又要比消防入去救<br />\n不如唔好放啦 <br />\n<br />\n以後你地自己打飛機<br />\n嘉年華遊行<br />\n嗌兩下唱吓歌仔就算啦 dllm<br />\n<br />\n邊度有贏過 輸到貼地"}]}